node.text: So much of my inspiration in climbing and life has come from incredible women who came before me. Their stories of grit, passion, and creativity were a pivotal part of the paths I chose in my own life. Such stories have a ripple effect that spread throughout our society and continue to inspire future generations ✨ Proud to take part in this conversation with my biggest supporter and favorite human @adrianballinger to honor @imyourwomanmovie premiering Friday Dec. 11th on @amazonprimevideo #imyourwoman

node.title: Amazon Studios I'M YOUR WOMAN Conversation Series

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᴇᴍɪʟʏ ʜᴀʀʀɪɴɢᴛᴏɴ on August 21, 2021 tagging @thenorthface, and @emilyaharrington. May be an image of one or more people and nature.

node.text: It’s Global Climbing Day!! From the gym to the tallest walls, climbing has the ability to teach us who we are, what we are capable of, and connect us with one another. I’ll be celebrating climbing and the community it creates today @earthtreksrockville (straight from 🇰🇬🥳🤯😌) !!! See you there DC friends! // @thenorthface // @thenorthface_climb // #wallsaremeantforclimbing // #globalclimbingday // 📸 @jonglassberg / @louderthan11

node.text: A sign of a good trip when you already miss everyone - especially this guy, and we are only parting for a day 😂😭🥰 // thank you @adrianballinger for being the best supporter, teammate, lover, and friend through all the lows and the highs🎢 I love you so much! // #tgronlocation // 📸 @griffinkerwin
